        "content": "## Setup\n1. Attach a Basic Auth credential to the Webhook node\n2. In \"Build Survey Link\", replace the Google Form ID and email entry ID (use your form's \"Get pre-filled link\")\n3. Add SMTP credential + sender email on the email node\n4. Add Telegram bot credential + chat ID\n5. In SF Integration Center, create an outbound integration to the webhook URL, mapping: Email, FirstName, LastName",
